name: iris-sample-data
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.1.0" %}

package:
    name: iris-sample-data
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    url: https://github.com/SciTools/iris-sample-data/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: 370066e5e43e8aa0c3ae9d7ef727fc1e28f11a5f965bc7864846013599df8135

build:
    noarch: python
    number: 0
    script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - pip
    run:
        - python

test:
    imports:
        - iris_sample_data

about:
    home: https://github.com/SciTools/iris-sample-data
    license: Open Government
    summary: 'Iris sample data.'

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
        - bjlittle
        - dkillick
